REQUIREMENTS
===========

Ruby 1.6.2
Gtk+ 2.0.0
GdkPixbuf 2.0
Ruby/GTK2

INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
====================

$ ruby extconf.rb /location/of/ruby-gtk/source/directory
$ make
# make install
$ ruby sample/test.rb some_image

